Hue is awesome, great recommendations
Dec 2023 • Family
Hue is a very knowledgeable, accommodating and professional guide. Our family of 12 did a private 8hr long tour of lady Buddha, marble mountain and old Hoi A town with him including lunch at a yummy noodle shop. He even made a reservation for our New Year’s Eve dinner at an exciting spot in old town. Highly recommend him!
Written December 31, 2023
Passenger18993228953
2 contributions
2.0 of 5 bubbles
Visit My Son, do not use this tour
I am sorry to say I cannot recommend this package, as it is not really a package. It is just a ride from the hotel to My Son. No guide or temple tickets as the listing implies. At over $100, the price is absurd. You csn easily use a Grab taxi for half the price.
My Son is worth visiting, but wear sturdy shoes with a good grip.
Do not eat at the restaurant at entrance (as our "guide" told us to do before he left us on our own). Food is mediocre at best. Service is poor. Go inside and get a drink and Banh Mi.
