Excellent Danang Tour Guide
Excellent English speaking and pleasant tour guide and very accommodating to family travelling with children and senior citizen. Very accommodating and efficient in terms of tour ideas/choices. Took 2 tour packages for group of 6 pax (Bana Hills and LingUng-Hoi An) and no regrets. Highly recommended. Transportation provided was spacious and clean. Tour guide was also an excellent photographer.
